AVID ELECTRONICS said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 27.50% to NT$3,610,000 from NT$4,979,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             3,610            4,979     
YOY%             -27.50%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales             23,383           15,851    
YOY%              47.52% 
=================================================================
 